# Assets Loans And Receivables Total Amount

## identifier
de8861

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of amounts receivable by the reporting party as determined in accordance with accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.Total.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.05
- period=instant
